  "2026-04-07T08:10:14.911Z",codex-agent,"Duplicate-check evidence commands: pm context --limit 10; pm list-open --limit 50; pm search get json body include-body complete details --limit 10. Net-new because no active item directly captures this false-positive clarification and regression-hardening scope."
  "2026-04-07T09:06:43.065Z",codex-agent,"Completed get --json body-shape clarification and hardening: documented that JSON get responses use deterministic top-level shape { item, body, linked, claim_state } and that body is top-level (not item.body). Updated README, docs/ARCHITECTURE, and get help tips, and added release-readiness regression assertion that body is present at top-level while item body remains front-matter only. Verification passed via focused integrations (cli.integration/help-runtime/release-readiness), full sandboxed test suite, and full sandboxed coverage run."
